99-0605 (La. 4/23/99)

STATE of Louisiana v. Brian J. ROSSI. No. 99-KK-0605. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 23, 1999.

IN RE: State of Louisiana; — Plaintiffs); Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs; Parish of Jefferson 2nd Parish Court Number 61-7053; to the Court of Appeal, Fifth Circuit, Number 98-KH-1253

Denied.

LEMMON, J. not on panel. VICTORY, TRAYLOR, and KNOLL, JJ. would grant the writ.
